---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const seo = {"title": "Threads — Smooth Threads | D‑Essence Wellness", "description": "Subtle collagen‑stimulating threads to refine and firm skin.", "canonical": "/services/smooth-threads", "type": "website", "ogImage": "/og-default" };
---

<BaseLayout {...seo}>

<section class="relative isolate bg-neutral-50 text-neutral-900">
  <!-- HERO: Oversized, single column -->
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 pt-28 md:pt-32 pb-10">
    <nav class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-3">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-neutral-800">Home</a>
      <span class="mx-1">/</span>
      <a href="/services" class="hover:text-neutral-800">Services</a>
      <span class="mx-1">/</span>
      <span class="text-neutral-800">Threads — Smooth Threads</span>
    </nav>
    <h1 class="text-[2.75rem] md:text-6xl leading-tight font-semibold tracking-tight">Threads — Smooth Threads</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-neutral-700 max-w-3xl">Subtle collagen‑stimulating threads to refine and firm skin.</p>
    <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-neutral-300 bg-white px-3 py-1 text-xs text-neutral-700">Consultation‑first</span>
      <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-neutral-300 bg-white px-3 py-1 text-xs text-neutral-700">Personalized plan</span>
      <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-neutral-300 bg-white px-3 py-1 text-xs text-neutral-700">Clear aftercare</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- STRIPE 1: Overview -->
  <div class="bg-white border-y border-neutral-200">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-12">
      <div class="flex items-baseline gap-4">
        <span class="text-neutral-300 text-4xl font-semibold select-none">01</span>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Overview</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">
        A refined, educational approach centered on natural‑looking results and comfort. We map your concerns,
        select the right technique/product or device, and share clear expectations for before, during, and after.
      </p>
      <blockquote class="mt-6 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-6 text-neutral-800">
        “Subtle, harmonious changes that respect your features and goals.”
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- STRIPE 2: What it treats (definition list) -->
  <div class="bg-neutral-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-12">
      <div class="flex items-baseline gap-4">
        <span class="text-neutral-300 text-4xl font-semibold select-none">02</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">What it treats</h3>
      </div>
      <dl class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm">
          <dt class="text-neutral-900 font-medium">Common targets</dt>
          <dd class="text-neutral-700 mt-1">Mapped to your anatomy and concerns.</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm">
          <dt class="text-neutral-900 font-medium">Approach</dt>
          <dd class="text-neutral-700 mt-1">Balance, proportion, and a natural finish.</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm">
          <dt class="text-neutral-900 font-medium">Comfort</dt>
          <dd class="text-neutral-700 mt-1">Technique and pacing to keep you at ease.</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm">
          <dt class="text-neutral-900 font-medium">Expectations</dt>
          <dd class="text-neutral-700 mt-1">Realistic timelines and maintenance as needed.</dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- STRIPE 3: Who it's for / Not for (vertical marker) -->
  <div class="bg-white border-y border-neutral-200">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-12">
      <div class="flex items-baseline gap-4">
        <span class="text-neutral-300 text-4xl font-semibold select-none">03</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Who it’s for / Who should avoid</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 relative">
        <div class="absolute left-1/2 top-2 bottom-2 hidden md:block w-px bg-neutral-200"></div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-5">
          <p class="text-neutral-900 font-medium">A good fit</p>
          <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-neutral-700 list-disc pl-5">
            <li>Healthy individuals with realistic expectations</li>
            <li>Concerns aligned with the service</li>
            <li>Open to aftercare and maintenance</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-5">
          <p class="text-neutral-900 font-medium">Consider alternatives</p>
          <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-neutral-700 list-disc pl-5">
            <li>Certain medical conditions or medications</li>
            <li>Active infections/irritation in the area</li>
            <li>Unrealistic timelines or expectations</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-neutral-500">Educational only—not medical advice. Review your history with your provider.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- STRIPE 4: How it works (three big steps) -->
  <div class="bg-neutral-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-12">
      <div class="flex items-baseline gap-4">
        <span class="text-neutral-300 text-4xl font-semibold select-none">04</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">How it works</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-500">Step 1</p>
          <p class="text-neutral-900 font-medium mt-1">Consult & planning</p>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm mt-1">Goal setting, mapping, tailored plan.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-500">Step 2</p>
          <p class="text-neutral-900 font-medium mt-1">Treatment</p>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm mt-1">Technique matched to indication and area.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-500">Step 3</p>
          <p class="text-neutral-900 font-medium mt-1">Aftercare</p>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm mt-1">Clear guidance and next steps.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- STRIPE 5: Results & Longevity (tiles) -->
  <div class="bg-white border-y border-neutral-200">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-12">
      <div class="flex items-baseline gap-4">
        <span class="text-neutral-300 text-4xl font-semibold select-none">05</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Results & longevity</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-5"><p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Onset</p><p class="text-neutral-900 font-medium mt-1">Varies by service</p></div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-5"><p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Peak</p><p class="text-neutral-900 font-medium mt-1">Discussed at consult</p></div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-5"><p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Duration</p><p class="text-neutral-900 font-medium mt-1">Maintenance as advised</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- STRIPE 6: Safety & Aftercare (checklist) -->
  <div class="bg-neutral-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-12">
      <div class="flex items-baseline gap-4">
        <span class="text-neutral-300 text-4xl font-semibold select-none">06</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Safety & aftercare</h3>
      </div>
      <ul class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-neutral-800 list-disc pl-5">
        <li>Follow your personalized post‑care handout</li>
        <li>Protect the area; avoid irritants as directed</li>
        <li>Hydration, rest, and recommended products only</li>
        <li>Report unexpected reactions promptly</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- STRIPE 7: FAQs (accordion) -->
  <div class="bg-white border-t border-neutral-200">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-12">
      <div class="flex items-baseline gap-4">
        <span class="text-neutral-300 text-4xl font-semibold select-none">07</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">FAQs</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-4 space-y-4">
        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-4">
          <summary class="font-medium text-neutral-900 cursor-pointer">How many sessions will I need?</summary>
          <p class="mt-2 text-neutral-700">It varies by concern and modality. Your provider will outline a personalized plan and maintenance if appropriate.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-4">
          <summary class="font-medium text-neutral-900 cursor-pointer">Will it look natural?</summary>
          <p class="mt-2 text-neutral-700">Our approach focuses on subtle, harmonious changes that complement your features.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="group rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-4">
          <summary class="font-medium text-neutral-900 cursor-pointer">Is there downtime?</summary>
          <p class="mt-2 text-neutral-700">Most services have minimal downtime. Temporary redness, swelling, or sensitivity can occur and usually resolves quickly.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-6 text-neutral-500 text-sm">*Informational content only; not medical advice. Individual results vary.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
